{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"adb5a3de-d1cb-4fa6-bf92-2e8312994808","content":"CLR activation logs won't help here. They diagnose **runtime loading/selection** issues (e.g., wrong CLR version picked, runtime fails to load). They don't contain information about managed exceptions like `NullReferenceException`.\n\nA `NullReferenceException` is a bug in your application code — something is `null` when you try to use it.\n\n**To diagnose it, you'd want to:**\n1. Check the **stack trace** from the exception — it tells you exactly which line caused it.\n2. Use a **debugger** (Visual Studio, `dotnet-dump`, or `lldb`) to inspect the state.\n3. Enable **first-chance exception** logging if the crash happens before you can attach.\n\nCan you share the **exception stack trace** or a **crash dump**? That would let me pinpoint the bug.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"11418bee-d3e7-4459-a68b-14eba870e03f","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking me to analyze CLR activation logs to diagnose a NullReferenceException in their .NET app. Let me check if there's a relevant skill for this.\n\nLooking at the available skills, I see \"clr-activation-debugging\" which is described as: \"Diagnoses .NET Framework CLR activation issues using CLR activation logs (CLRLoad logs) produced by mscoree.dll.\"\n\nHowever, I need to think about whether this is actually the right tool. The user has a NullReferenceException, which is a managed exception - not a CLR activation issue. CLR activation logs deal with things like:\n\n\n- The shim picking the wrong runtime\n- Failing to load any runtime\n- Unexpected .NET 3.5 Feature-on-Demand dialogs\n- Loading both v2 and v4 into the same process\n\nA NullReferenceException that occurs after the app has started is a runtime bug in the application code itself, not a CLR activation problem. CLR activation logs won't help diagnose this kind of issue, so I should explain to the user why this skill isn't the right fit rather than using it.","outputTokens":461,"requestId":"600B:14524E:D6BFEC:F81D5B:69EAC717"},"id":"affddef9-6a9d-41c2-94cc-cd2f0cac827e","timestamp":"2026-04-24T01:28:05.823Z","parentId":"5bfb9f1d-f379-4cca-bc6b-b4beaff0af61"}
